CompanyDescription.label: Company Description
CompanyDescription.value: In 2022, Complete Solar and Solaria came together with a vision to drive a clean, all-electric future powered by the sun. The combination of these two leading U.S. residential solar companies deliver enhanced capabilities to enable one-stop service from design to installation and financing of a customer's complete solar and clean energy needs.
